ablo|Escobar: Loving Pablo]]''\n| June 20, 2018\n| {{flagicon|Spain}}\n| distribution only; produced by Escobar Films and B2Y Productions\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BjWytXZAhGi/|title=Escobar opens in June 20, 2018 in cinemas|publisher=VIVA International Pictures|website=[[Instagram]]|date=June 27, 2018|accessdate=May 29, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Adrift (2018 film)|Adrift]]''\n| June 27, 2018\n| {{flagicon|United States}}\n| distribution only; produced by [[Lakeshore Entertainment]], [[Ingenious Media]], [[RVK Studios]], [[Huayi Brothers|Huayi Brothers Pictures]], and [[STXfilms]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/Bkg6NVNgCL8/|title=Adrift opens in June 27, 2018 in cinemas|publisher=VIVA International Pictures|website=[[Instagram]]|date=June 27, 2018|accessdate=September 12, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Kickboxer: Retaliation]]''\n| July 11, 2018\n| {{flagicon|United States}}\n| distribution only; produced by Our House Films and Acme Rocket Fuel\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BkphmWOg0sF/|title=Kickboxer: Retaliation opens in July 11, 2018 in cinemas|publisher=VIVA International Pictures|website=[[Instagram]]|date=June 30, 2018|accessdate=September 12, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Billionaire Boys Club (2018 film)|Billionaire Boys Club]]''\n| July 18, 2018\n| {{flagicon|United States}}\n| distribution only; produced by Armory Films\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/Bk4jGabg-EG/|title=Billionaire Boys Club opens in July 18, 2018 in cinemas|publisher=VIVA International Pictures|website=[[Instagram]]|date=July 6, 2018|accessdate=September 12, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Behind the Walls''\n| July 25, 2018\n| {{flagicon|United States}}\n| distribution only; produced by Dual Visions and Roaming Elephant Productions\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/Bk4dyolAef8/|title=Behind the Walls opens in July 25, 2018 in cinemas|publisher=VIVA International Pictures|website=[[Instagram]]|date=July 6, 2018|