RELEASE DATE OF THE FILM \u2013 only put the release date of the film if it is officially announced by the production company or the news/article you have been put as sourced. If the film release date has not been announced, indicate or put it as \"TBA\" shortened for \"To be announced\".\n\n\u2022 EVERYTHING YOU HAVE BEEN CONTRIBUTED HERE WILL REFLECT TO THE PERSON WHO SEARCHES, VIEWS, VISITS, AND CHECKS THE ARTICLES FROM ALL OVER THE WORLD. IT IS IMPORTANT THAT WE CONTRIBUTE RELIABLY SO THAT WE CAN PROMOTE OUR OWN ENTERTAINMENT INDUSTRY.\n\n\u2022 THIS NOTE IS APPLICABLE TO THE ARTICLES OF FILM PRODUCTION OF THE PHILIPPINES HERE IN WIKIPEDIA\u2013BOTH ENGLISH AND TAGALOG.\n\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\n;Color key\n{{plainlist|\n* {{Color box|#FFFACD|border=darkgray}} \u2013 a foreign film distributed by Viva International Pictures\n* {{Color box|#FFFFFF|border=darkgray}} \u2013 Film(s) that are not colored/white colored are regular release in the cinemas and is not an entry to any film festival inside or outside the country.\n}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" \n|-\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Film <!--ALWAYS PUT IT IN ORDER OF THE RELEASE DATE-->\n! style=\"width:15%;\"| Release\n! style=\"width:60%;\"| Notes\n|-\n|-\n|''[[Pedro Penduko (film)|Pedro Penduko]]''\n| 2020\n| co-production with Epik Studios<ref>[http://news.abs-cbn.com/entertainment/08/10/17/its-confirmed-james-reid-is-the-new-pedro-penduko It's confirmed: James Reid is the new Pedro Penduko]. ''ABS-CBN News''. Published on 2017-08-10. Retrieved 2017-08-11.</ref>\n|-\n|''Osyana''\n|2020\n|co-production with Epik Studios\n|-\n|''Delta''\n|TBA\n|\n|-\n| ''The Nurse''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://push.abs-cbn.com/2017/10/7/fresh-scoops/watch-nadine-lustre-reveals-her-future-projects-169524|title=Nadine Lustre reveals her future projects|publisher=[[ABS-CBN]]|website=PUSH|date=October 7, 2017|time=10:58 AM|author=Leary, Joan|accessdate=